            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1583501638362-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>meat-free chick'n jalfrezi</strong> over the <strong>jeera rice</strong></p><p>Tip: For fancy presentation, press the rice into a small bowl and turn out</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
